values: Thank you for downloading Evacuation, a mod made for the 2023 New Horizons modding jam! Please play on an existing save file.
A new exhibit has been added to the museum.

Heliostudy contains developer commentary that can be enabled from the options menu.

It is highly recommended to complete the mod before enabling commentary.

Thanks for downloading Tesseract's Secret!
Check your ship log to begin!

MINDSCAPES:
A new exhibit has been added to the observatory.
A new adventure awaits you starting at the Vessel!
Thank you for downloading Fret's Quest! Someone is waiting for you in the Village near the geysers.

Thanks for downloading Reflections! This mod was made for the 2024 New Horizons Single Planet Mod Jam.

Use of the Suit Log mod is highly recommended.
The Quasar Project has a certain mechanic that is graphically intensive; when you reach it, you can adjust its quality in the mod settings.
